10 AND ZONING REGULATIONS; TO PROHIBIT A MUNICIPALITY
11 FROM ENFORCING BUILDINGS AND ZONING REGULATIONS ON
12 COUNTY PROPERTY; AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES.
